    "description": {
      "value": "<p>The sage transforms his ki into a tangible needle and thread he can use to stitch wounds. As a standard action, the sage can spend 1 ki point to heal himself or an adjacent target of an amount of hit point damage equal to 3 x his class level. If the sage is at least 5th level, the target is also healed of 1 point of ability damage, plus 1 additional point of ability damage for every 3 class levels he possesses. This ability can be used to reattach severed limbs, as long as the original limb is available, removing any effects or penalties attributed with the limbs&#8217; loss.</p>\n<h3 id=\"toc56\"><span><span style=\"color: #00c000\">Ki Blaster Esoteries</span></span></h3>\n",
